manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 7-in-1 Toddler Car Toys - Perfect Pink and Purple Princess Foldable Transport Carrier Truck Set for Girls 3 4 5 Years Elevate your little one's playtime with our 7-in-1 Toddler Car Toys set. Designed with toddlers in mind, this set includes 1 foldable transport truck and 6 mini colorful pull-back cars, all adorned with charming princess bowknot shapes and delightful cartoon patterns. Highly popular among girls aged 1 2 3 4 5 years and beyond, these toys offer versatile play options.

Interactive Play Options for Toddler Car Toys Simply give the transport truck a gentle push, and it will transport the mini cars on an exciting journey. Transform the carriage into a long track for thrilling races, and adjust the truck's head to change the route. Press the bow button to activate cheerful music and flashing lights, promoting visual and auditory development without being too noisy or bright for sensitive little ones.

Upgrade the Gameplay:Toddler Car Toy with 2 Play Modes Freight Mode: 6 small cars can be loaded into the container, which has three levels with space for two cars on each level. Simply raise the barrier to secure the cars. Let little girls pull the truck, transporting cars to their desired destinations! Track Mode: Upon reaching the destination, convert the container into a track to unload the small cars. The small cars can then race on the track, providing an exciting unloading experience. Once the cars have departed, convert the track back into a container, and the truck is ready to go, completing a full transportation cycle. Note：To prevent fingers from being pinched when the container is opened and closed, children under 3 years old should be supervised by adult.

Soft Material and High-Quality Crafted from top-notch, non-toxic plastic with a smooth contour and no sharp edges, these toys are designed for small hands, enhancing imagination and hand-eye coordination.

Imaginative Toddler Car Toys for Little Princesses Packaged in an adorable pink princess-themed design, they make unique and ideal gifts for girls aged 1 2 3 4 5 years, perfect for various occasions, including holidays, Christmas, and 1st birthdays. Upgrade playtime with these high-quality, girl-centric toys that are sure to bring extra joy to your little princess. Package Included 1 × Foldable Transport Carrier Truck 6 × Mini pull-back Cars Note: Lighting and music require 2 AAA batteries (Not included)
